d upon. (will get your post edited/deleted and a telling off from the moderators)<br><br>a) Posting to the wrong forum. We have a number of different forums for a reason. Please post in the correct place.<br><br>b) Cross Posting. Never post the same thing in more than 1 forum.<br><br>c) Violation of the signature rules.<br><br>d) Posting all in capitals. Especially thread titles. Threads all in caps WILL be deleted.<br><br>3) Signatures must be kept below 50kb in size. Flash/shockwave animations are allowed, as long as they are below this size. Remember, not everyone is on broadband.<br><br>4) Scripts that produce 'mouse-over' graphical effects on images in signatures are not allowed, as they have been proven to cause problems for some users.<br><br>5) A signature should be no deeper than 10 lines of text, including images, and should not be so wide as to cause the window to extend on a 800x600 display.<br><br>6) Under no circumstance should sound be included in any thread, and this includes signatures.<br><br>Continued violations of rules in the above section can and will result in a warning, and possibly a ban.<br><br>The main rule is this:<br><br>Remember this is a game that we play to have fun. Posting here should be just as enjoyable for all users, as playing EQ.<br><br>The above posting ruled have been copied from, and used with permission by Zadkiel, from www.monkly-business.com<br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugilfalas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gilfalas</A> at: 6/4/02 10:36:29 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uriggorsmortus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RiggorsMortus</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com